{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-01632/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-01632"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:16:32"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["exterior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman drive in a car at night."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-01632","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-01632"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1/f5c7ee1c-dedc-477b-b8a4-7c2da8a6b23e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:38:33.795Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Once again, Reynolds drives his car somewhat recklessly. The pair race along the country road, leaving behind them traces of passing trees and buildings in the light emitted from the car’s taillights. Reynolds’s excitement manifests in his handling of the car, and the speed at which they travel and the focus on their faces with light trailing behind them represent how they’re barreling into a new life together.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The pace of Reynold’s driving also evokes the euphoria of falling in love: vertiginous, dynamic, and sometimes dangerous.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:434.1048034934498,512.3034934497816,431.94323144104806,485.3711790393013"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1/6e0e2815-5d85-470e-b40e-23235ea01670","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:38:46.245Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>These car scenes bring to mind <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW223556852 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ltwX603Ft4\"><u>those in Stanley Kubrick’s </u><em><u>A Clockwork Orange</u></em></a><em> </em>(1971).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01632/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:18.318777292576378,42.56550218340607,191.94323144104806,126.75764192139738"}}}]}]}]}